<p>Mojitos aren't available in Brazil, and definitely not in Rio. What they do have is stuff like Guaraná Antarctica, Coca-Cola/Pepsi, and Fanta Uva/Laranja.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Does Rio de Janero even have beaches?</p>
